{"word":"G4717 - σταυρόω - stauróō - stow-ro'-o - Crucify","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σταυρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">stauróō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">stow-ro'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Crucify</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிலுவையில் அறை"},{"paragraph":"1. to stake, drive down stakes"},{"paragraph":"2. to fortify with driven stakes"},{"paragraph":"3. to crucify"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4716 - σταυρός - staurós - stow-ros'/4716\">G4716</a>; to <i>impale</i> on the cross; figuratively to <i>extinguish</i> (<i>subdue</i>) passion or selfishness: - crucify.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}